NAME
    Wikibase::Datatype::Print - Wikibase datatype print helpers.

SYNOPSIS
     use Wikibase::Datatype::Print::Item qw(print);

     my $pretty_print_string = print($obj, $opts_hr);
     my @pretty_print_lines = print($obj, $opts_hr);

DESCRIPTION
    This distributions is set of print helpers for Wikibase::Datatype
    objects.

SUBROUTINES
  "print"
     my $pretty_print_string = print($obj, $opts_hr);
     my @pretty_print_lines = print($obj, $opts_hr);

    Construct pretty print output for main objects like
    Wikibase::Datatype::Item, Wikibase::Datatype::Lexeme,
    Wikibase::Datatype::Mediainfo and Wikibase::Datatype::Property.

    Returns string in scalar context. Returns list of lines in array
    context.

ERRORS
     print():
             Unsupported Wikibase::Datatype object.
                     Reference: %s

